name: The New Universe
description: Metaverses, VR, and blockchains are opening portals to the new universe. One of unlimited reach, potential, and use. Endless virtual worlds to explore, borderless connections with others, and new means of commerce. All from our computers and mobile devices, and emerging VR and AR gear. Grab this NFT to show you believe in the future of metaverses before they really take off!
